    SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`
    FROM `Product` AS `p`
    ORDER BY `p`.`Id`
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS `t`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `t`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `t`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id`

LEFT JOIN `Product` AS `p` ON `c`.`Id` = `p`.`CategoryId`
ORDER BY `c`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`

        SELECT t.Id, t.Amount, t.CustomerName, t.Date, t.PaymentMethod, t.SellerId, t.Status, s0.Id, s0.ProductId, s0.Quantity, s0.SalesRecordId
